Description: Discover the perfect travel companion with the TRAWOC Travel Backpack. Designed for both men and women, this stylish backpack offers a generous 40 litre capacity, making it an ideal backpack for 2-3 days trip or a quick weekend getaway. It measures 59 cm x 33 cm x 20 cm, providing ample space for your essentials. This large backpack for men and women features one large main compartment for your clothes and a padded laptop sleeve suitable for a 15.6-inch laptop. The two zipper pockets provide additional storage for smaller items and documents. Meanwhile, both side water bottle pockets ensure you stay hydrated during your trip. Crafted from premium quality fabric, this backpack bag is designed to withstand the rigors of travel. The water-resistant fabric protects your belongings, while the integrated 100% waterproof rain cover, stored in a separate pocket, offers an extra layer of protection during inclement weather. Comfort is at the forefront of this backpack’s design. It boasts a breathable mesh padded back panel and fully adjustable shoulder straps, ensuring comfort during extended periods of wear. With its premium quality YKK zippers, buckles, and clips, you can trust that the TRAWOC Travel Backpack will stand the test of time. Plus, it comes with a 3-year manufacturer warranty for peace of mind. Whether you're using it as a laptop backpack for the office, a trekking hiking backpack for your next adventure, or a big size bag for a tourist tour, this backpack is versatile and durable. Experience the convenience and comfort of travelling with the TRAWOC Travel Backpack.
